  "detailed_description": "<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2650080/extras/247f712d8aa18b80c012e28f75c381c3.poster.avif?t=1719832311\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2650080/extras/247f712d8aa18b80c012e28f75c381c3.webm?t=1719832311\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CHANGE THE RULES</h2>Change the rules you're following by equipping various rulebooks. <br>Why would you slash your enemies with a sword? <br>Beat your enemies with a bow throw your sword at them and propel yourself forward with bombs. <i>That's what this game is about.</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2650080/extras/bf928c09f6f03775d0014224440e6821.poster.avif?t=1719832311\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2650080/extras/bf928c09f6f03775d0014224440e6821.webm?t=1719832311\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ROUGELIKE, HACK&SLASH ADVENTURE</h2>Hack and slash through mobs and other idiots trying to complete their own idiotic journey.<br>Each <strong>death </strong>means a new fresh world to conquer and a new hero to conquer it.<br><strong>Different </strong>items to acquire, <strong>different </strong>enemies to defeat, and <strong>different </strong>lands to conquer can be all found in each run!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2650080/extras/428c57aae6faa08abee463c8f5a5a7c1.poster.avif?t=1719832311\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2650080/extras/428c57aae6faa08abee463c8f5a5a7c1.webm?t=1719832311\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Online & Local Multiplayer (NO LIMIT)</h2>Gather friends and foes online or locally with Split-Screen or even <u> join with your friends on local split-screen to an online game! </u><br><strong> You want to divide your screen into 1000 squares? Then by my guest! There is no limit on the split-screen multiplayer, go wild with dividing your screen!</strong> <br>Cooperate or rival in conquering this idiotic roguelike world. In the end, only one idiot can rule the world but why not cooperate with others and betray them in the very end? <br>That is also an option...<br><br>",
