ce src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2650080/extras/428c57aae6faa08abee463c8f5a5a7c1.webm?t=1719832311\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Online & Local Multiplayer (NO LIMIT)</h2>Gather friends and foes online or locally with Split-Screen or even <u> join with your friends on local split-screen to an online game! </u><br><strong> You want to divide your screen into 1000 squares? Then by my guest! There is no limit on the split-screen multiplayer, go wild with dividing your screen!</strong> <br>Cooperate or rival in conquering this idiotic roguelike world. In the end, only one idiot can rule the world but why not cooperate with others and betray them in the very end? <br>That is also an option...<br><br>",
